title: Second Date Update: Roofer Madness
itunes:title: Second Date Update: Roofer Madness
description: Meeting someone at a coffee shop in broad daylight should be a totally normal date... But for the guy on the phone, it was one he doesn't remember. He only has some recollection of what happened and needs our help figuring out if it was the best or worst date of his life!
